dXWn6ZyI/AAAAAAAADl8/rBfj2DPrwBQ/s1600/IMG_0581.jpg" height="320" width="213" /></a></div><br /><table align="center" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" class="tr-caption-container" style="margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; text-align: center;"><tbody><tr><td style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-h0Q9zCnDIow/U69dZLAk5LI/AAAAAAAADmE/ek-baGFg5ws/s1600/IMG_0583.jpg" imageanchor="1" style="margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;"><img border="0" src="http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-h0Q9zCnDIow/U69dZLAk5LI/AAAAAAAADmE/ek-baGFg5ws/s1600/IMG_0583.jpg" height="213" width="320" /></a></td></tr><tr><td class="tr-caption" style="text-align: center;">an "Aztec"-styled skyscraper</td></tr></tbody></table><br /><table align="center" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" class="tr-caption-container" style="margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; text-align: center;"><tbody><tr><td style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-Mz5qr6OHLU0/U69dcUo-SXI/AAAAAAAADmU/xPMMhOBZxV8/s1600/IMG_0594.jpg" imageanchor="1" style="margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;"><img border="0" src="http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-Mz5qr6OHLU0/U69dcUo-SXI/AAAAAAAADmU/xPMMhOBZxV8/s1600/IMG_0594.jpg" height="213" width="320" /></a></td></tr><tr><td class="tr-caption" style="text-align: center;">Lafayette Park</td></tr></tbody></table><br /><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"><a href="http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-TkqV01Szubk/U69deciqJfI/AAAAAAAADmc/EHBorcJkepo/s1600/IMG_0596.jpg" imageanchor="1" style="margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;"><img border="0" src="http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-TkqV01Szubk/U69deciqJfI/AAAAAAAADmc/EHBorcJkepo/s1600/IMG_0596.jpg" height="213" width="320" /></a></div><br /><div>I hope I'll be back sometime in the future, to see how things change and to see more of the city!<br /><br /><i>Postscript July 11th: &nbsp;Here's a nice <a href="http://www.nytimes.com/2014/07/13/magazine/the-post-post-apocalyptic-detroit.html">NYTimes piece</a> on how things are going in Detroit today.</i></div></div>
